\begin_inset Formula $y\in\Y$
\end_inset

, and is Lipschitz continuous in 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

, uniformly in 
\begin_inset Formula $y,$
\end_inset

 with Lipschitz constant 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\norm{K(x,y)-K(x^{\prime},y)}{2}\leq L\norm{x-x^{\prime}}{2}\qquad\forall(x,y),(x^{\prime},y)\in\X\times\Y.
\]

\end_inset


