\begin_layout Proof
As 
\begin_inset Formula $W_{2}$
\end_inset

 metrizes weak convergence, take 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{n}\rightharpoonup\rho$
\end_inset

.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\vert E(\rho_{n})-E(\rho)\vert & \leq\left\lvert \int\mu(dy)\left[\log\rho K(y)-\log\rho_{n}K(y)\right]\right\rvert +\alpha\left\lvert \int\left[\rho_{n}(dx)\log\rho_{n}(x)-\rho(dx)\log\rho(x)\right]\right\rvert ,
\end{align*}

\end_inset

since 
\begin_inset Formula $x\mapsto K(x,y)$
\end_inset

