\begin_layout Standard
Consider the functional 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
E(\rho)= & \KL(\mu,\rho K)-\alpha\ent(\rho)\\
=- & \int\mu(dy)\log\rho K(y)-\alpha\ent(\rho)-\ent(\mu),
\end{align*}

\end_inset

the last term, 
\begin_inset Formula $\ent(\mu)$
\end_inset

