\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{-\delta\ent}{\delta\rho}\left(\rho\right)=1+\log\rho\label{eq:subdifferential_entropy}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

is a sub-differential for 
\begin_inset Formula $-\ent(\rho)$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
after "Lemma 8"
key "carrillo2006contractions"
literal "true"

\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

